skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: nuts inn more
des: Ask Alexa to "open, Nuts N' More" and she’ll respond with a randomly-selected snack that incorporates one of the many high protein Nuts ‘N More spreads. However, the best part is that you can ask for as many snack ideas as your tastebuds can handle.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
